#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiriki; is an addictive and fun dice game by &kde;, designed to be played "
"by as many as six players. Participants have to collect points by rolling "
"five dice for up to three times per single turn. Each roll generates a "
"specific combination of numbers which the player is free to either accept or "
"decline. However, each specific combination of numbers can be accepted only "
"once. After thirteen turns the game ends and the scores are compared. The "
"player with the largest amount of points wins the game."
msgstr ""
"&kiriki; je zasvojljiva in zabavna igra s kockami &kde;, zasnovana za "
"igranje do šestih igralcev. Udeleženci morajo zbirati točke z metanjem petih "
"kock do trikrat na posamezen obrat. Vsak obrat ustvari določeno kombinacijo "
"številk, ki jo igralec lahko sprejme ali zavrne. Vsaka posebna kombinacija "
"številk pa je lahko sprejeta le enkrat. Po trinajstih obratih se igra konča "
"in rezultati se primerjajo. Igralec z največjim številom točk zmaga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Earn more score points than either of the opponents."
msgstr "Zaslužite si več točk kot katerikoli nasprotnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once &kiriki; starts, it right away gives out the first combination for the "
"player one. If you are the player one, then it is now your turn, otherwise "
"you will have to wait until all other players make their moves."
msgstr ""
"Ko se eEnkrat &kiriki; začne, takoj izda prvo kombinacijo za igralca ena. Če "
"ste prvi igralec, ste zdaj na vrsti vi, sicer boste morali počakati, da vsi "
"ostali igralci opravijo svoje poteze."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:78 index.docbook:80 index.docbook:84 index.docbook:86
#: index.docbook:241 index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Opomba:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, unless the game settings have been changed, and in single player "
"mode, the first player is controlled by human (you), while all other five "
"players are controlled by Artificial Intelligence."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto, razen če so bile nastavitve igre spremenjene, in v načinu enega "
"igralca, prvega igralca nadzira človek (vi), medtem ko vseh ostalih pet "
"igralcev nadzira umetna inteligenca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once it is your turn, the first thing you should do is examine the current "
"roll. Each of the five dice on the left hand side of the game screen has a "
"specific value. Check the sequence to see if these values form any of the "
"score patterns."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste na vrsti, morate najprej pregledati trenutni krog. Vsaka od petih "
"kock na levi strani igralnega zaslona ima določeno vrednost. Preverite "
"zaporedje, da vidite, ali te vrednosti tvorijo katerega od vzorcev "
"rezultatov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80 index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The detailed description of the score pattern values can be found in the "
"<link linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Game Rules, Strategies and Tips</link> "
"section of this handbook."
msgstr ""
"Podroben opis vrednosti vzorca rezultatov je na voljo v razdelku <link "
"linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti</link> v tem "
"priročniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep in mind that the combination can match more than one score pattern. In "
"this case you will have to determine which score pattern will result in "
"greater points for you."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da se lahko kombinacija ujema z več kot enim vzorcem "
"rezultatov. V tem primeru boste morali določiti, kateri rezultatski vzorec "
"vam bo prinesel več točk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case the current sequence matches no score pattern, or matches a score "
"pattern you have already used up, you have two more rolls to fix the "
"situation. To use your second (third) roll select the dice you are not "
"satisfied with by clicking on them with your mouse and click the "
"<guibutton>Roll</guibutton> button located right under the dice. This will "
"cause the dice in question to reroll, thus changing their values."
msgstr ""
"Če se trenutno zaporedje ne ujema z nobenim vzorcem rezultatov ali se ujema "
"z vzorcem rezultatov, ki ste ga že porabili, imate na voljo še dva meta, da "
"popravite situacijo. Če želite uporabiti svoj drugi (tretji) met, izberite "
"kocke, s katerimi niste zadovoljni, tako da kliknete nanje z miško in "
"kliknete gumb <guibutton>Vrzi</guibutton>, ki se nahaja tik pod kocko. To bo "
"povzročilo, da se bo zadevna kocka ponovno vrgla, s čimer se bodo spremenile "
"njihove vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have done the third reroll you must choose the score pattern which "
"fits the dice sequence on hand. If none of the score patterns fit the "
"sequence - you can either use <guilabel>Chance</guilabel> score pattern, or "
"just select any score pattern on your scoreboard."
msgstr ""
"Ko opravite tretji ponovni met, morate izbrati rezultatski vzorec, ki "
"ustreza zaporedju kock na roki. Če nobeden od vzorcev rezultatov ne ustreza "
"zaporedju - lahko uporabite vzorec rezultata <guilabel>Naključje</guilabel> "
"ali preprosto izberete kateri koli vzorec rezultatov na vaši tabeli "
"rezultatov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a score pattern that does not fit current dice sequence, the "
"score pattern you select will become void and of zero value."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete rezultatski vzorec, ki ne ustreza trenutnemu zaporedju kock, bo "
"izbrani rezultatski vzorec postal neveljaven in brez vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As soon as you choose the score pattern its value updates to reflect the "
"dice sequence you currently have."
msgstr ""
"Takoj ko izberete vzorec rezultata, se njegova vrednost posodobi, da odraža "
"zaporedje kock, ki ga trenutno imate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right after that your turn ends and the next participant’s turn begins. This "
"sequence repeats some thirteen times and then the game ends, the scores are "
"calculated and the high scores are awarded."
msgstr ""
"Takoj za tem se konča vaša vrsta in začne na vrsti naslednji udeleženec. To "
"zaporedje se ponovi približno trinajstkrat, nato pa se igra konča, rezultati "
"se izračunajo in podelijo najvišji rezultati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules"
msgstr "Pravila igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiriki; score board is divided into fourteen different lines. Each line "
"holds a single score pattern and the players' score earned for a roll "
"matching the pattern. The score pattern of each line is calculated as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"&kiriki; semafor je razdeljen na štirinajst različnih vrstic. Vsaka vrstica "
"vsebuje en vzorec rezultatov in rezultat, ki ga igralci zaslužijo za met, ki "
"se ujema z vzorcem. Rezultatski vzorec vsake vrstice se izračuna na "
"naslednji način:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>1s</guilabel>: Sum of all dice valued ‘1’."
msgstr "<guilabel>1s</guilabel>: Vsota vseh kock z vrednostjo \"1\"."

