#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Bonus if > 62</guilabel>: Player is awarded an additional 35 "
"points if the summarized value of all the field above is greater than 62 "
"points."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Bonus, če je > 62</guilabel>: Igralec prejme dodatnih 35 točk, če "
"je skupna vrednost vseh zgornjih polj večja od 62 točk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Upper Total</guilabel>: It is not a playable field, but only a "
"summary of all the fields above."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zgornja vsota</guilabel>: To ni polje za igranje, ampak le "
"povzetek vseh zgornjih polj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>3 of a Kind</guilabel>: Summarized value of dice when three of the "
"dice are bearing the same value."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>3 enake vrste</guilabel>: Povzetek vrednosti kock, ko imajo tri "
"kocke enako vrednost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '14121'. The sum is: '9'='1'+'1'+'1'+'4'+'2'. Dice on "
"display: '55151'. The sum is: '17'='5'+'5'+'5'+'1'+'1'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '14121'. Vsota je: '9'='1'+'1'+'1'+'4'+'2'. Prikazana "
"kocka: '55151'. Vsota je: '17'='5'+'5'+'5'+'1'+'1'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>4 of a Kind</guilabel>: Summarized value of dice when four of the "
"dice are bearing the same value."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>4 enake vrste</guilabel>: Povzetek vrednosti kock, ko imajo štiri "
"kocke enako vrednost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '41444'. The sum is: '17'='4'+'4'+'4'+'4'+'1'. Dice on "
"display: '22522'. The sum is: '13'='2'+'2'+'2'+'2'+'5'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '41444'. Vsota je: '17'='4'+'4'+'4'+'4'+'1'. Prikazana "
"kocka: '22522'. Vsota je: '13'='2'+'2'+'2'+'2'+'5'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Full House</guilabel>: 25 points are awarded to the player if the "
"round results in three dice of a kind and a pair."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Full House</guilabel>: 25 točk prejme igralec, če se v krogu "
"izkažejo tri kocke enake vrste in par."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dice on display: '11212'. Dice on display: '53353'."
msgstr "Prikazana kocka: '11212'. Prikazana kocka: '53353'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Small Straight</guilabel>: 30 points are awarded to the player if "
"the round results in four dice of sequential value."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Small Straight</guilabel>: 30 točk prejme igralec, če krog "
"povzroči štiri kocke zaporedne vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '14312'. The sequence is: '1','2','3','4'. Dice on display: "
"'51643'. The sequence is: '3','4','5','6'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '14312'. Zaporedje je: '1','2','3','4'. Prikazana kocka: "
"'51643'. Zaporedje je: '3','4','5','6'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Large Straight</guilabel>: 40 points are awarded to the player if "
"the round results in five dice of sequential value."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Large Straight</guilabel>: 40 točk prejme igralec, če krog "
"povzroči pet kock zaporedne vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '34152'. The sequence is: '1','2','3','4','5'. Dice on "
"display: '53264'. The sequence is: '2','3','4','5','6'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '34152'. Zaporedje je: '1','2','3','4','5'. Prikazana "
"kocka: '53264'. Zaporedje je: '2','3','4','5','6'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>&kiriki;</guilabel>: 50 points are awarded to the player if the "
"round results in five dice of the same value. You can score as many &kiriki; "
"as you get, for each one after the first you get an additional turn at the "
"end of the game."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>&kiriki;</guilabel>: 50 točk prejme igralec, če krog povzroči pet "
"kock enake vrednosti. Dosežete lahko toliko &kiriki; ko dobite, za vsakega "
"po prvem dobite dodaten korak na koncu igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dice on display: '11111'. Dice on display: '33333'."
msgstr "Prikazana kocka: '11111'. Prikazana kocka: '33333'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Chance</guilabel>: Summarized value of all the dice currently on "
"display."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Možnost</guilabel>: Povzetek vrednosti vseh trenutno prikazanih "
"kock."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '51143'. The sum is: '14'='5'+'1'+'1'+'4'+'3'. Dice on "
"display: '21526'. The sum is: '16'='2'+'1'+'5'+'2'+'6'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '51143'. Vsota je: '14'='5'+'1'+'1'+'4'+'3'. Prikazana "
"kocka: '21526'. Vsota je: '16'='2'+'1'+'5'+'2'+'6'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Lower Total</guilabel>: It is not a playable field, but only a "
"summary of all the fields starting from <quote>3 of a Kind</quote> and lower."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Nižja vsota</guilabel>: To ni igralno polje, ampak samo povzetek "
"vseh polj, ki se začnejo od <quote>3 </quote> in manj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Grand Total</guilabel>: It is not a playable field, but only a sum "
"of <quote>Upper Total</quote> and <quote>Lower Total</quote> fields."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Grand Total</guilabel>: To ni polje za igranje, ampak le vsota "
"polj <quote>Zgornji seštevek</quote> in <quote>Spodnji seštevek</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other rules and constrains:"
msgstr "Druga pravila in omejitve:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "The entire game round is split into 13 turns."
msgstr "Celoten krog igre je razdeljen na 13 potez."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each player can do one to three rolls of dice per turn."
msgstr "Vsak igralec lahko vrže enega do tri kocke na potezo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the first roll is done, a player can perform additional rolls for up "
"to two times (three rolls at all per turn)."
msgstr ""
"Po končanem prvem metu lahko igralec izvede dodatne mete največ dvakrat "
"(vsega tri mete na potezo)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Player is not obligated to perform additional rolls if the first roll "
"brings satisfactory results."
msgstr ""
"Igralec ni dolžan izvesti dodatnih metov, če prvi met prinese zadovoljive "
"rezultate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each additional roll may either involve all the dice, or only the selected "
"ones."
msgstr "Vsak dodatni met lahko vključuje vse kocke ali samo izbrane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A Player can select the dice to be recast by clicking on them with the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Igralec lahko izbere kocke za preoblikovanje tako, da jih klikne z miško."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the dice have been recast their previous value is lost and only the new "
"value is valid."
msgstr ""
"Ko so kocke ponovno vržene, se njihova prejšnja vrednost izgubi in velja "
"samo nova vrednost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result of the roll is considered satisfactory if the values of the dice "
"on display can be put into one of the score patterns discussed above."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat meta se šteje za zadovoljivega, če se vrednosti prikazanih kock "
"lahko uvrstijo v enega od zgoraj obravnavanih vzorcev točkovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each individual score pattern can only be used once per game per player. "
"Therefore, once the score pattern has been used by one player it can no "
"longer be used by that same player. However, another player can still use "
"it, unless he has used this same pattern up already."
msgstr ""
"Vsak posamezen rezultatski vzorec se lahko uporabi samo enkrat na tekmo na "
"igralca. Torej, ko en igralec uporabi rezultatski vzorec, ga ta isti igralec "
"ne more več uporabiti. Vendar ga lahko še vedno uporablja drug igralec, "
"razen če je ta isti vzorec že uporabil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts a new game."
msgstr "Začne novo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show High Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži najboljše rezultate</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Shows the high score list.</action> When your current game score "
"exceeds one the top ten scores listed, you are prompted to add your name."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže seznam najboljših rezultatov.</action> Ko vaš trenutni "
"rezultat igre preseže enega od desetih najboljših na seznamu, boste pozvani, "
"da dodate svoje ime."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prints current score board."
msgstr "Natisne trenutno tablo z rezultati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &kiriki;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &kiriki;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Namig</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Give a hint by highlighting one or more dices to roll or a row on the score "
"board. Using this feature the score will not be considered as a high score."
msgstr ""
"Dajte namig tako, da označite eno ali več kock, ki jih želite vreči, ali "
"vrstico na semaforju. Z uporabo te funkcije rezultat ne bo upoštevan kot "
"visok rezultat."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Play a demo game. To stop the demo mode start a new game."
msgstr "Igrajte demo igro. Če želite ustaviti demo način, zaženite novo igro."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kiriki; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kiriki; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kiriki; does not currently feature any themes."
msgstr "Ne. &kiriki; trenutno ne vsebuje nobene teme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Naredil sem napako. Ali jo lahko razveljavim?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kiriki; has no <quote>Undo</quote> option."
msgstr "Ne. &kiriki; nima možnosti <quote>Razveljavi</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. The game of &kiriki; cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ne. Igre &kiriki; ni mogoče igrati s tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne morem ugotoviti, kaj naj naredim tukaj! Ali obstajajo namigi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To learn about the game play rules and tactics please read the <link linkend="
"\"rules_and_tips\">Game Rules, Strategies and Tips</link> section of this "
"handbook."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvedeti več o pravilih in taktikah igre, preberite razdelek <link "
"linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti</link> v tem "
"priročniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. There is no <quote>Save</quote> feature in &kiriki;."
msgstr "Ne. V &kiriki; ni funkcije <quote>Shrani</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "The AI is too fast! I cannot see what it is doing!"
msgstr "Umetna inteligenca je prehitra! Ne vidim, kaj počne!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change Artificial Intelligence's speed of action please use the game "
"configuration dialog discussed in the <link linkend=\"configuration\">Game "
"Configuration</link> section of this handbook."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti hitrost delovanja umetne inteligence, uporabite "
"pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo igre, ki je obravnavano v razdelku <link "
"linkend=\"configuration\">Konfiguracija igre</link> v tem priročniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Game Configuration</title>"
msgstr "<title>Konfiguracija igre</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Game Configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija igre</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kiriki; configuration dialog lets you configure the number of "
"participants, manage their identities, and their response times."
msgstr ""
"&kiriki; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno vam omogoča, da konfigurirate "
"število udeležencev, upravljate njihove identitete in njihove odzivne čase."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the response times for Artificial Intelligence driven players "
"only."
msgstr ""
"Odzivne čase lahko spremenite samo za igralce, ki jih poganja umetna "
"inteligenca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Number of players:</guilabel> this field defines the number of "
"players for &kiriki;. The values allowed here range between two and six."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Število igralcev:</guilabel> to polje določa število igralcev za "
"&kiriki;. Tukaj so dovoljene vrednosti med dvema in šestimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>1.</guilabel>-<guilabel>6.</guilabel> Numbered fields are the "
"identities of the participating players. You can change their names as well "
"as specify whether they will be human controlled, or driven by the "
"Artificial Intelligence. To define who controls the player use a check box "
"located on the right hand side, right next to the name entry box."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>1.</guilabel>-<guilabel>6.</guilabel> Oštevilčena polja so "
"identitete sodelujočih igralcev. Spremenite lahko njihova imena in določite, "
"ali jih bo upravljal človek ali jih bo vodila umetna inteligenca. Če želite "
"določiti, kdo nadzira igralca, uporabite potrditveno polje na desni strani, "
"tik ob polju za vnos imena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "The first player must always be human controlled."
msgstr "Prvi igralec mora biti vedno pod človeškim nadzorom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes to number of participants and their identities will be applied on "
"the next game."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe števila udeležencev in njihovih identitet bodo uporabljene pri "
"naslednji igri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Delay between computers move (msec):</guilabel> lets you specify "
"the delay between Artificial Intelligence's turns. The value of this field "
"is zero by default, meaning that the Artificial Intelligence reacts "
"instantaneously."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zakasnitev med premikanjem računalnikov (msec):</guilabel> vam "
"omogoča, da določite zakasnitev med obrati umetne inteligence. Vrednost tega "
"polja je privzeto enaka nič, kar pomeni, da se umetna inteligenca odzove "
"takoj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum value for this field is 999 milliseconds."
msgstr "Največja vrednost za to polje je 999 milisekund."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Font Size:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Row Height:</guilabel> to "
"adjust the score board to your liking."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Velikost pisave:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Višino vrstice:"
"</guilabel>, da prilagodite semafor po svojih željah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to play immediately at &kiriki; startup disable the default "
"option <guilabel>Show demonstration game at startup</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite takoj igrati na &kiriki; ob zagonu onemogočite privzeto možnost "
"<guilabel>Pokaži predstavitveno igro ob zagonu</guilabel>."

